OL,3,CDebt collector given innocent person's
OL,4,Cdetails in mistaken identity case
OL,6,FThe Parish of Grouville (POG) has been
OL,7,Fformally warned by Jersey's data
OL,8,Fregulator after it mistakenly shared
OL,9,Fthe wrong person's details with a debt
OL,10,Fcollector.
OL,12,FLocal officials incorrectly identified
OL,13,Fan innocent member of the public who
OL,14,Fhappened to have the same name as the
OL,15,Fresident owing taxes.
