OL,6,FFollowing the investigation, the
OL,7,Fregulator ruled that the parish must
OL,8,Freview the rates tax process to
OL,9,F"ensure it is fit for purpose" and has
OL,10,F"appropriate checks to identify
OL,11,Findividuals responsible for payments".
OL,13,FStaff must then be trained on this
OL,14,Fsystem and the POG has to update its
OL,15,FPrivacy Policy to properly reflect how
OL,16,Fit processes people's data.
OL,18,FThe JOIC says these orders have since
OL,19,Fbeen completed.
