OL,6,FIn response, Grouville Constable Mark
OL,7,FLabey explains: "Whilst the parish
OL,8,Ffully accepts the shortcomings within
OL,9,Four data protection compliance
OL,10,Fframework, no member of the current
OL,11,Fstaff at Grouville Parish Hall were
OL,12,Finvolved in this incident.
OL,14,F"They are fully cognisant of the
OL,15,Frelevant procedures to follow in all
OL,16,Fmatters, and I have every confidence
OL,17,Fin them to do so.
OL,19,F"They remain an excellent team and at
OL,20,Fthe heart of parish life."
